entries.question: when and where were you born, introduce yourself, use 100 words
entries.answer: I was born on June 6th, 1999, in a small town in upstate New York. I grew up surrounded by nature, and spent most of my time outside exploring the woods and streams near my house. I developed a love for the outdoors at a young age, and continue to enjoy hiking, camping, and kayaking. In addition to my love of nature, I also enjoy playing the violin and am a member of my school's symphony orchestra. I am a hard worker
